quran[25{c,v,t}:
20,13,"aur mein ne tujh ko chuun liya hai, sun jo kuch wahi kya jata hai"
20,14,"mein hi Allah hon, mere siwa koi khuda nahi hai, pas to meri bandagi kar aur meri yaad ke liye namaz qaim kar"
20,15,"qayamat ki gharri zaroor anay wali hai mein uss ka waqt makhfi rakhna chahta hon, taakay har mutnaqas apni sae ke mutabiq badla paye"
20,16,"pas koi aisa shakhs jo uss par imaan nahi lata aur apni khwahish nafs ka bandah ban gaya hai tujh ko uss gharri ki fikar se nah rok day, warna to halakat mein par jaye ga"
20,17,"aur ae moose, yeh tairay haath mein kya hai? """
20,18,"moose ne jawab diya"" yeh meri laathi hai, is par take laga kar chalta hon, is se apni bakrion ke liye pattay جھاڑتا hon, aur bhi bohat se kaam hain jo is se laita hon """
20,19,"farmaya"" pheink day is ko moose """
20,20,is ne pheink diya aur yakayak woh aik saanp thi jo daud raha tha
20,21,"farmaya"" pakar le is ko aur dar nahi, hum usay phir waisa hi kar den ge jaisi yeh thi"
20,22,"aur zara apna haath apni baghal mein daba, chamakta howa niklay ga baghair kisi takleef ke yeh doosri nishani hai"
20,23,is liye ke hum tujhe apni barri nishanain dikhaane walay hain
20,24,"ab to firaon ke paas ja, woh sarkash ho gaya hai """
20,25,"moose ne arz kya"" parvar-digaar, mera seenah khol day"
20,26,aur mere kaam ko mere liye aasaan kar day
20,27,aur meri zabaan ki girah Suljha day
20,28,taakay log meri baat samajh saken
20,29,aur mere liye mere apne knbe se aik wazeer muqarrar kar day
20,30,"haroon, jo mera bhai hai"
20,31,uss ke zareya se mera haath Mazboot kar
20,32,aur is ko mere kaam mein shareek kar day
20,33,taakay hum khoob teri paki bayan karen
20,34,aur khoob tera charcha karen
20,35,"to hamesha hamaray haal par nigran raha hai """
20,36,"farmaya"" diya gaya jo to ne manga ae moose"
20,37,hum ne phir aik martaba tujh par ahsaan kya
